Package fi.grimripper.loww.movement

Contains classes and interfaces directly related with movement.

See: Description

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    MotionListener
    Interface for observing moving objects on a tile grid.
    MovementModifier
    Anything that implements this interface can affect various aspects of movement.
    MoveModeListener
    A listener interface to observe changes in a mobile object's collection of movement modes.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    DefaultMovement
    This is the default movement implementation, which progresses outward from a starting position.
    DefaultMovement.PathData
    A data object to store movement data relevant to a single tile in a path.
    MobileObject
    A mobile object is an obstacle that can move.
    MovementMode
    The base class for movement modes.
